column1: Ribosome profiling RNA sequencing in the low dose cpeb1b MO injected wt and cpeb1b mutant zebrafish embryos Overall design: Ribo-seq of 6 samples from the low dose cpeb1b MO injected wt zebrafish embryos and 6 samples from the low dose cpeb1b MO injected Cpeb1b mutant zebrafish embryos at 8 hpf, 16 hpf, and 22 hpf.
